data.description: Marco Island south-facing pool home in sought-after Tigertail neighborhood! Open floor plan, 3 bedrooms and 2 baths with screened lanai and sparkling pool in one of Marco Island's most desirable locations. Large 100x110 lot. Close to Esplanade, shopping, restaurants, Veteran's Community Park (seasonal farmer's market, concerts) and more. Only .8 of a mile to Tigertail beach entrance. Watch the adorable native burrowing owl nest right in the front yard and bald eagle sanctuary down the street! New roof in 2016. Flood insurance is current. No flooding in Hurricane Ian. Water did not enter garage or house. Priced below recent appraisal. Unique opportunity to buy under a $million in this prestigious neighborhood! A/C 3 years old, shingle roof 7 years old.
